-- Giants’ Win Over Cowboys Is Most Watched Sunday Night Game in NBC History
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2012-01-02T16:58:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-02/giants-win-over-cowboys-is-most-watched-sunday-night-game-in-nbc-history.html
The  New York Giants ’ 31-14 National
Football Conference East Division-clinching win over the  Dallas
Cowboys  last night on NBC drew the highest overnight rating in
the network’s six years of broadcasting Sunday night games.  The Giants victory was seen in 17.1 percent of U.S. homes
in the top 56 metered television markets, NBC said in a
statement citing  Nielsen Media Research . It eclipsed the  New
York Jets ’ season-opening defeat of the Cowboys, which
registered a 16.9.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  